    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_548b4ed2-c5a2-4a7e-b046-5b6a5a44b3e1" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can mention another course member in a discussion reply in Discussions Redesign.</p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li>Mentioning users is not supported in anonymous discussions. </li>
<li>Mentioning users is related to a <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/t5/Canvas-Resource-Documents/Canvas-Course-Role-Permissions/ta-p/387080" target="_blank">course role permission</a>. If you are not able to mention users, the required permission may not be enabled for your role.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussions" data-step-uuid="3c83cc93-ddfc-425d-a86f-bb986dcf87bb">
    <h2 id="open_discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussions</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/732/331/original/332ae903-9b46-4212-a4bc-2a9ba5979737.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussions " height="280" width="179">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_a2237ac7-f291-4d2e-82f4-0fd80d5eff20" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion_topic" data-step-uuid="2a082424-7952-49a1-952e-0983a34d1240">
